  "title": "Low-fat-friendly Liver Portuguese foie-gras Paella",
  "description": "This umami-packed paella dish features tender foie-gras, juicy liver, and a medley of low-fat-friendly ingredients, all perfectly balanced in a single pan. Serve hot and enjoy!",
