  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter in a large paella pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chicken stock and bring to a boil.",
    "Add the foie gras and liver, and cook for 5 minutes or until the liver is browned.",
    "Add the saffron, smoked paprika, cumin powder, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the Spanish rice and green beans, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes or until the rice is tender and the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with lemon wedges if desired."
